Package: gitr
Title: Lightweight API for Git
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Stu",
           family = "Field",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "stu.g.field@gmail.com",
           comment = c(ORCID = "YOUR-ORCID-ID"))
Description: A light-weight, dependency-free, API to access
    system-level 'git' commands from within R. Contains wrappers
    and defaults for common data science workflows as well as
    Z-shell plugin aliases. Generalized API syntax is also available.
